<title>USA: AMEX to list options on BEA Systems July 29.</title>
<headline>AMEX to list options on BEA Systems July 29.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-07-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>The American Stock Exchange said Wednesday it will list options July 29 on stock of BEA Systems Inc.</p>
<p>Its options will open with strike prices at 15, 17-1/2 and 20 and position limits of 7,500 contracts. Initial expiration months will be August, September and December 1997 plus March 1998.</p>
<p>LETCO-Specialist LP will be specialist for the options.</p>
<p>BEA Systems, based in Sunnyvale, Calif., provides software used by large organizations. ((DerivativesDesk(312)408-8750)) E-mail:derivatives@reuters.com</p>
